#### [NEW] `features/rooms/pages/rooms-list/rooms-list.component.ts`
- Component that fetches all rooms on init.
- [openAddModal()](file:///c:/PI%20AMMAR/Esprit-PiProject-4SAE8-2026-CertifyPro/frontend/src/app/features/users/pages/users-list/users-list.component.ts#82-97) / [openEditModal(room)](file:///c:/PI%20AMMAR/Esprit-PiProject-4SAE8-2026-CertifyPro/frontend/src/app/features/users/pages/users-list/users-list.component.ts#98-112) / `closeModal()`.
- `saveRoom()` → calls create or update.
- [deleteRoom(id, name)](file:///c:/PI%20AMMAR/Esprit-PiProject-4SAE8-2026-CertifyPro/backend/services/user-service/src/main/java/com/training/platform/service/RoomService.java#48-51) → confirm dialog before deleting.

#### [NEW] `features/rooms/pages/rooms-list/rooms-list.component.html`
- Page header with "Add Room" button.
- Loading spinner.
- Data Table: columns for Name, Capacity, Projector, Computers, Whiteboard, Status (Available/Unavailable), Actions.
- Add/Edit modal with all Room fields, including boolean toggles for equipment.

#### [NEW] `features/rooms/pages/rooms-list/rooms-list.component.css`
- Reuse same CSS variables as [users-list.component.css](file:///c:/PI%20AMMAR/Esprit-PiProject-4SAE8-2026-CertifyPro/frontend/src/app/features/users/pages/users-list/users-list.component.css) (they use CSS custom properties like `var(--primary)` from the global [styles.css](file:///c:/PI%20AMMAR/Esprit-PiProject-4SAE8-2026-CertifyPro/frontend/src/styles.css)).
- Add status badge styles for Available / Unavailable.

#### [NEW] `features/rooms/rooms.routes.ts`
- Defines route: `{ path: 'rooms', component: RoomsListComponent }`.

#### [MODIFY] [admin.routes.ts](file:///c:/PI%20AMMAR/Esprit-PiProject-4SAE8-2026-CertifyPro/frontend/src/app/features/admin/admin.routes.ts)
- Import and spread `...roomsRoutes` inside `adminRoutes`.

#### [MODIFY] Admin sidebar/layout
- Add a "Rooms" navigation link to the admin layout sidebar, pointing to `/admin/rooms`.

